                <h1>Do Background Checks Show Job Titles? Understanding Employment Verification</h1>
                <p>Yes, background checks can reveal a person's job titles from previous employment, as employers often verify the information provided on resumes. However, the depth of the check may vary based on the company's practices. Always ensure that you have permission before conducting any background check.</p>
